    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK111">
<l>takuti yeṉavoṉṟu naṉṟē pakutiyāṟ</l>
<l>pāṟpaṭ ṭoḻukap peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That virtue alone is called propriety, if one attain to act</l>
<l>as is befitting towards each faction.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
